0000 times is for the protection from oppressors and the dictators.", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "YAA KHAAFE-ZO ka 70000 martaba vird karna zaalimo’n aur sitam-gaaro’n se muhaafizat (hifaazat) ka baais hai.", "UrduDescription": "’’یَاخَافِضُ‘‘ کا 70000 بار ورد کرنا ظالموں اور ستمگروں سے محافظت کا باعث ہے۔ ", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1020878, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": 2, "EnglishDescription": "If a person fears a powerful enemy then he should enclose himself with the zikr of YAA KHAAFE-ZO, this can be done by 3 days fast (without gap) and do iftar with the halaal food, eat very less, and in those days recite YAA KHAAFE-ZO frequently, than again fast on the 4th day and go in a lonely place recite 2 rakat namaz like fajr than facing qibla recite YAA KHAAFE-ZO 70000 times than do the prostration (sajdah) and ask Allah (swt) protection from that enemy, inshallah will be fulfilled.", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Jo shakhs taaqat-war dushman ka khouf rakhta ho us ko chahiye keh YAA KHAAFE-ZO ke ism (naam) ka apne gird hisaar (diwaar) bana le, is ka tareeqa yeh hai keh 3 Din musalsal (continue) roza rakkhe aur halaal se iftar kare, kam se kam khaaye, un ayyaam (dino) mein YAA KHAAFE-ZO ka bohot ziyadah vird kare, phir chauthay (4th) din roza rakkhe aur kisi tanhaayi ke maqaam par ja kar 2 rakat namaz padhe aur qibla rukh ho kar 70000 martaba YAA KHAAFE-ZO ka vird kare phir sajdeh mein sar rakh kar Khuda se us dushman se muhaafezat (hifaazat) maange, inshallah apni muraad pa lega.", "UrduDescription": "جو شخص طاقتور دشمن کا خوف رکھتا ہو اس کو چاہئے کہ ’’یَاخَافِضُ‘‘  کے اسم کا اپنے گرد حصار بنالے اس کا طریقہ یہ ہے: 3 دن لگا تار روزہ رکھے اور حلال سے افطار کرے، کم سے کم کھائے، ان ایام میں ’’یَاخَافِضُ‘‘  کا بہت زیادہ ورد کرے پھر چوتھے روز روزہ رکھے اور کسی تنہائی کے مقام پر جا کر ۲ رکعت نماز پڑھے اوررو بقبلہ ہوکر 70000 بار ’’یَاخَافِضُ‘‘  کا ورد کرے پھر سجدہ میں سر رکھ کر خدا سے اس دشمن سے محافظت مانگے، انشاء اللہ اپنی مراد پالے گا۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null,